  <entry>
    <title>C#学习日记(3)</title>
    <url>/2024/08/15/Csharp%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E6%97%A5%E8%AE%B0-3/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="If语句"><a href="#If语句" class="headerlink" title="If语句"></a>If语句</h1><figure class="highlight c#"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="keyword">var</span>)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>若<code>var = ture</code>则执行if语句大括号下的代码，若<code>var = false</code>则反之</p>
<h2 id="else语句"><a href="#else语句" class="headerlink" title="else语句"></a>else语句</h2><figure class="highlight c#"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> <span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="keyword">var</span>)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span>（var_2）</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>以上是一个<code>如果 如果则 否则</code>语句，要注意的是如果其中有某组语句运行成功，就不会执行值后的语句，如<code>var = ture</code> <code>if</code>下大括号下的代码执行成功，则不会执行<code>else if</code>和<code>else</code>里的代码</p>
<h1 id="运算符-不等运算符"><a href="#运算符-不等运算符" class="headerlink" title="运算符 &amp;  不等运算符"></a>运算符 &amp;  不等运算符</h1><h2 id="运算符"><a href="#运算符" class="headerlink" title="运算符(&#x3D;&#x3D;)"></a>运算符(&#x3D;&#x3D;)</h2><p>如果运算符 (&#x3D;&#x3D;)两边操作数的值相等，则相等运算符 (&#x3D;&#x3D;) 返回 true，否则返回 false</p>
<h2 id="不等运算符"><a href="#不等运算符" class="headerlink" title="不等运算符(!&#x3D;)"></a>不等运算符(!&#x3D;)</h2><p>如果不等运算符运算符 (!&#x3D;)操作数相等，则不等运算符 (!&#x3D;) 返回 false，否则，返回 true</p>
<h1 id="小作品"><a href="#小作品" class="headerlink" title="小作品"></a>小作品</h1><p>昨天小作品的完善版——简单四则运算计算器</p>
<figure class="highlight c#"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> System;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Program</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="function"><span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Main</span>()</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        Console.WriteLine(<span class="string">&quot;请输入需要使用的运算方式:&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">string</span> YSFF  = Console.ReadLine();<span class="comment">//这里的变量名取自&quot;运算方法&quot;的拼音首字母</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (YSFF == <span class="string">&quot;加法&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            Console.WriteLine(<span class="string">&quot;请输入第一个加数&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">int</span> x;</span><br><span class="line">            x = Convert.ToInt32(Console.ReadLine());</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            Console.WriteLine(<span class="string">&quot;请输入第二个加数&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">int</span> y;</span><br><span class="line">            y = Convert.ToInt32(Console.ReadLine());</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">int</span> z;</span><br><span class="line">            z = x + y;</span><br><span class="line">            Console.WriteLine(<span class="string">&quot;计算结果为:&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            Console.WriteLine(z);</span><br><span class="line">            Console.WriteLine(<span class="string">&quot;按任意键推出...&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            Console.ReadKey();</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (YSFF == <span class="string">&quot;减法&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        &#123; </span><br><span class="line">            Console.WriteLine(<span class="string">&quot;请输入被减数&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">int</span> x;</span><br><span class="line">            x = Convert.ToInt32(Console.ReadLine());</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            Console.WriteLine(<span class="string">&quot;请输入减数&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">int</span> y;</span><br><span class="line">            y = Convert.ToInt32(Console.ReadLine());</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">int</span> z;</span><br><span class="line">            z = x - y;</span><br><span class="line">            Console.WriteLine(<span class="string">&quot;计算结果为:&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            Console.WriteLine(z);</span><br><span class="line">            Console.WriteLine(<span class="string">&quot;按任意键推出...&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            Console.ReadKey();</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (YSFF == <span class="string">&quot;乘法&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            Console.WriteLine(<span class="string">&quot;请输入第一个乘数&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">int</span> x;</span><br><span class="line">            x = Convert.ToInt32(Console.ReadLine());</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            Console.WriteLine(<span class="string">&quot;请输入第二个乘数&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">int</span> y;</span><br><span class="line">            y = Convert.ToInt32(Console.ReadLine());</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">int</span> z;</span><br><span class="line">            z = x * y;</span><br><span class="line">            Console.WriteLine(<span class="string">&quot;计算结果为:&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            Console.WriteLine(z);</span><br><span class="line">            Console.WriteLine(<span class="string">&quot;按任意键推出...&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            Console.ReadKey();</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span>(YSFF == <span class="string">&quot;除法&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            Console.WriteLine(<span class="string">&quot;请输入被除数&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">int</span> x;</span><br><span class="line">            x = Convert.ToInt32(Console.ReadLine());</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            Console.WriteLine(<span class="string">&quot;请输入除数&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">int</span> y;</span><br><span class="line">            y = Convert.ToInt32(Console.ReadLine());</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">int</span> z;</span><br><span class="line">            z = x / y;</span><br><span class="line">            Console.WriteLine(<span class="string">&quot;计算结果为:&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            Console.WriteLine(z);</span><br><span class="line">            Console.WriteLine(<span class="string">&quot;按任意键推出...&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            Console.ReadKey();</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            Console.WriteLine(<span class="string">&quot;抱歉无法提供&quot;</span> + YSFF + <span class="string">&quot;该计算方法&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            Console.WriteLine(<span class="string">&quot;按任意键推出...&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">            Console.ReadKey();</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<p>有什么方法可以让程序运行完后在运行多次呢？想把这个计算器设计成重复运行多次的</p>
]]></content>
